# Build
# NOTE: Do not gitignore services/api/dist — Render omits gitignored paths from the
# deploy slug, so Nest's built output would be missing at runtime ("Cannot find module dist/main").
# Run `npm run build` in services/api before committing only if you intentionally ship artifacts (avoid).
